title: #87: Hammer and the Nail with Lee Camp
description:
Thank you for tuning for another episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli. This episode Sam and Ryan welcome the political pundit anarchist, Lee Camp. This episode we discuss...
1) Tin Foil Hat Comedy Night Live at San Fran's Cobb June 1st and Sacramento Punchline June 2nd
2)Lee Camp's New Comedy Special; Taping in Los Angeles
3) Michelle Wolf
4) The Main Stream Media
5) Wikileaks
6)Jimmy Dore
7)Tthe UN and FEMA Camps
thank you so much for all of your support.
